Rupesh Ranjan​

rupesh.ranjan@globaldata.com​

Types of captcha​

2​

​

SCOPE of this project​

3​

We are interested in decoding image based simple captcha using any image recognition software/tools​

SAMPLE sites using text captcha​

4​

PROBlem with existing solutions​

5​

OCR is complicated and specific to single type of captcha​

6​

Available libraries are not free ​

https://pypi.org/project/captcha-solver/​

7​

SINCE WE DEAL WITH VERY WIDE VARIETY OF WEB PAGES, WE CANNOT PREDICT THE IMAGE/FONT TYPE OF CAPTCHA. ​

Hence, BUILDING A CUSTOM OCR MODULE WITH TESSERACT ETC. IS ALSO NOT PRACTICALLY VIABLE SOLUTION​

​

Solution ???​
